Package: crontabR
Type: Package
Title: Easy Script Scheduling in R for Linux
Version: 0.2.2
Author: Eric Bailey
Maintainer: Eric Bailey <eb11307@gmail.com>
Description: Provides an interface to your personal crontab in R. Set R scripts
    to run at specific intervals. Use the RStudio addin for an easy graphical way to
    schedule tasks in R under a Linux environment.
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
Depends:
    shiny,
    miniUI,
    DT,
    lubridate
Suggests:
    mailR
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
